      h1 Last year, 43 million people came to Citizens Advice online to solve their personal problems.
      br

  .row.spacer
    .col-md-7.align-top
      h2 The problem
      p Citizens Advice help millions of people with benefits problems every year.
      p With more and more people looking for advice online, my team was tasked with replacing hundreds of long, complex and outdated pages.
      p To do this, we needed to gain a deep understanding of our audience and write concise, actionable advice to solve their problems as quickly as possible.
  .row.spacer
    .col-md-4
