  .row.spacer
    .col-md-7
      h2 Audit the content, understand the subject
      p To redesign an extensive, high-traffic area of advice content, we needed to understand exactly what it already covered.
      p It wasn't feasible to read through hundreds of pages of advice content, so I developed a system to summarise lengthy user journeys.
      p Using this technique, we skimmed through long sections as a group, quickly noting down the key advice offered on each page.

